/p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"б\" id=\"note7b\" data-full-marker=\"7б\">\n<p data-aid=\"123543459\" id=\"note7b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/rest?lang=rus\"><small>РСП</small> Покой</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"в\" id=\"note7c\" data-full-marker=\"7в\">\n<p data-aid=\"123543462\" id=\"note7c_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/num/14.23?lang=rus#p23\">Числ. 14:23</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/deut/1.35-37?lang=rus#p35\">Втор. 1:35–37</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.23-25?lang=rus#p23\">У. и З. 84:23–25</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"г\" id=\"note7d\" data-full-marker=\"7г\">\n<p data-aid=\"123543466\" id=\"note7d_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/nt/heb/3.8?lang=rus#p8\">Евр. 3:8</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"д\" id=\"note7e\" data-full-marker=\"7д\">\n<p data-aid=\"123543470\" id=\"note7e_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/num/26.65?lang=rus#p65\">Числ. 26:65</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/17.23-31?lang=rus#p23\">1 Неф. 17:23–31</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"8\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"а\" id=\"note8a\" data-full-marker=\"8а\">\n<p data-aid=\"123543473\" id=\"note8a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/rebellion?lang=rus\"><small>РСП</small> Восстание, мятеж</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"б\" id=\"note8b\" data-full-marker=\"8б\">\n<p data-aid=\"123543477\" id=\"note8b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/17.30?lang=rus#p30\">1 Неф. 17:30</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/12.36-37?lang=rus#p36\">Алма 12:36–37</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/hel/7.18?lang=rus#p18\">Гел. 7:18</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"в\" id=\"note8c\" data-full-marker=\"8в\">\n<p data-aid=\"